<p>
Thank you for choosing to make a gift to the Tufts OpenCourseWare (Tufts OCW) project.  We greatly welcome any financial contributions to Tufts OCW. Your $50, $100, or donation in any amount will enable us to continue offering a high-quality publication of Tufts course materials. 
Tufts OCW offers free and open access to many courses.  Faculty contribute their course curriculum materials for free. Your donation creates the funds necessary to prepare content, clear intellectual property rights and maintain the technology used in digital publishing.
</p>
<p>
Here's how to make your gift:
</p>
<p>
<span class="orange_title">Online Giving:</span><br/>
Use our secure form to make an <a href="http://www.tufts.edu/givenow">online gift</a> via credit card. Select "other" from the School menu and enter "OpenCourseWare Fund" to designate your gift.
</p>
<a class='btnLnk' href="http://www.tufts.edu/givenow">Support Tufts OCW</a>
<p>
<span class="orange_title">By Telephone:</span><br/>
You may also call our toll free number 866-351-5184 from anywhere in North America, or call 617-627-4705 within Massachusetts to make a gift via credit card.  
</p>
<p>
<span class="orange_title">By U.S. Mail:</span><br/>
If you prefer to mail your donation, please make your check payable to 'Trustees of Tufts College.'  Enclose a note indicating that the contribution is for the 'Tufts OpenCourseWare Fund' and address to:<br/>
Tufts University<br/>
 P.O. Box 3306<br/>
 Boston, MA 02241-3306<br/>
</p>

<div class="orange_title" style="margin-top:10px">
<i>Thank you for your gift.</i>
</div>
